output eDP-1 scale 2
output eDP-1 pos 0 0 res 3840x2160
output HDMI-A-1 scale 1
output HDMI-A-1 pos 1920 0 res 1920x1080
output HDMI-A-1 subpixel rgb
output * bg $wallpaper fill



